org.apache.ambari.server.events

Class UpgradeUpdateEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.events.STOMPEvent
      • org.apache.ambari.server.events.UpgradeUpdateEvent

  • public class UpgradeUpdateEvent
extends STOMPEvent
    Contains information about cluster upgrade state update. This update will be sent to all subscribed recipients. Used for messaging to UI.
